videos.description: Duke's Cassius Stanley and Louisville's Darius Perry get tangled on the court and have to be separated.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Stanley, Perry get heated on court) 2020/01/18

videos.headline: Stanley, Perry get heated on court

videos.description: Louisville's Dwayne Sutton grabs a rebound and dishes to Jordan Nwora, who's all alone to throw down the dunk.
videos.headline: Nwora throws down breakaway dunk

videos.description: Duke's Tre Jones grabs a steal and passes to Cassius Stanley, who goes skyward for the thunderous dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Stanley elevates for the powerful slam) 2020/01/18

videos.headline: Stanley elevates for the powerful slam

videos.description: Malik Williams throws down a posterizing dunk at the end of the second half, propelling Louisville to the 79-73 win vs. Duke.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Williams' poster dunk seals win for Louisville) 2020/01/18

videos.headline: Williams' poster dunk seals win for Louisville
